### Approach
The approach involves creating different heuristics using various mathematical and array operations. Each function will compute a priority score for each bin based on the item size and the current state of the bins. The operations used include exponential functions, trigonometric functions, standard deviation, mean, and other array manipulations. Each function is designed to be unique by combining these operations in different ways.

### Solution Code

