- Higher priority to bins that are less full.
- Higher priority to bins that are more full.
- Higher priority to bins with similar residual space to other bins.
- Etc.

### Combining Features:
- Multiply or add different features to create a composite score.
- Use exponential or logarithmic functions to scale the features.
- Use boolean masks to gate features (e.g., only consider features if the bin can fit the item).

