### Solution Code

```python
import numpy as np

def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item * (bins / (bins + 1))) * np.exp(item - bins) + (item - bins) * np.log(bins)

def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item * (item / (bins + 1))) * np.exp(item) + (item - bins) * np.log(bins)

