### Solution Code:

```python
import numpy as np

def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item * (bins + np.mean(bins))) + np.log(item + bins) + np.exp(item - bins) * np.sin(item - np.mean(bins))
```...
