### Solution Code

```python
import numpy as np

def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item * np.mean(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.log(item + bins) * np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) * 2
```

